  }, "v55"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i ch\u01B0a th\u1EADt bi\u1EBFt Ng\xE0i, nh\u01B0ng ta bi\u1EBFt Ng\xE0i. N\u1EBFu ta n\xF3i ta kh\xF4ng bi\u1EBFt Ng\xE0i, th\xEC ta c\u0169ng n\xF3i d\u1ED1i nh\u01B0 c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i. Nh\u01B0ng ta bi\u1EBFt Ng\xE0i v\xE0 v\xE2ng l\u1EDDi Ng\xE0i. "), mdx("h6", {
