  }, "v56"), mdx("p", null, "T\u1ED5 ti\xEAn c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i l\xE0 \xC1p-ra-ham, h\u1EDBn h\u1EDF mong \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c th\u1EA5y ng\xE0y ta \u0111\u1EBFn tr\u1EA7n gian. \xD4ng \u0111\xE3 th\u1EA5y v\xE0 m\u1EEBng r\u1EE1.\" "), mdx("h6", {
